OCF1xZWNd7ZgqdRLk/1/" rel=3D"sponsored">Bovada</a></strong>,
              to be around 96%.</strong>&nbsp; I've been able to see report=
s for
            millions of dollars of casino play at Bovada for 2022, with an =
RTP
            of 97.27%, but this includes table games which can have a highe=
r RTP
            (like blackjack, which is around 99.5% with proper play).&nbsp;=
 So
            an RTP of 96% for slots seems reasonable.</p>
          <p><br>
          </p>
          <h2>Cruise ship slot returns</h2>
          <p>A Wizard of Vegas member who says that he used to run casinos =
